<i>noun</i>: 태풍 [태풍] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>태풍 [태풍]</dt><br>
<dd>typhoon</dd><br>
<dd>주로 7~9월에 태평양에서 한국, 일본 등 아시아 대륙 동부로 불어오는, 거센 폭풍우를 동반한 바람.</dd><br>
<dd>The fierce wind accompanying a rainstorm, blown from the Pacific Ocean to the eastern part of the Asian continent such as Korea, Japan, etc., usually between July and September.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>